                <p class="ia-table-text">The NHM ‘presented’ baseline recycling rate is estimated to be 43.3%. It is likely that this is an overestimate which means that we might overestimate costs to businesses and underestimate carbon savings. However, this aligns with our cautious approach to estimating costs to businesses. The baseline is also adjusted to include the DRS effect.<b> </b> For Option 3M, we assume that 80% of the total tonnage that could be further recycled is presented by business. This is our central estimate. We also modelled 70% and 90% capture rates for low and high estimates, respectively. The high and low sensitivities also include familiarisation costs, lift prices and DRS effect. </p>
