              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">HH sector: dry recyclate material revenue </p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">There is some uncertainty related to material revenue prices, e.g. reduced contamination of dry materials could affect current prices. </p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">10% decrease</p>
              </td>
