            <tr>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">HH sector: vehicle and container capital</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">To align with the new requirements, local authorities will need to buy new vehicles and bin containers. This could create demand pressures. Both variables could have a significant impact on estimated capital costs for both the transition and post-transition period.</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">10% increase</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">10% decrease</p>
              </td>
