            <tr>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">HH sector: flatted property operational costs</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">There is a large variation in costs observed for flatted property collection schemes. The central analysis has been based on efficient costs. It is very unlikely that these costs could reduce further. Hence, a very small change for the high NPV scenario. </p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">Plus £23.05/hh/yr, from a central estimate of £16.95.</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">Minus £1.95/hh/yr, from a central estimate of £16.95.</p>
              </td>
