              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">Central modelling assumes 4 hours per manager are required to read and understand the new requirements; and 15 minutes per staff member are required to undertake training.</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">Assumes 8 hours for reading and understanding, and 20 minutes training. </p>
