            <tr>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">NHM sector: lift prices</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p class="ia-table-text">NHM lift prices could change as a result of new materials required to be recycled and/or increased route density (if, for example, the same contractor is able to win more contracts on the same round (economies of scale)). Lift prices are also dependent on gate fees which could change due to packaging recovery note values.</p>
                <p class="ia-table-text" />
                <p class="ia-table-text">NB we were not able to obtain any new evidence concerning lower NHM lift prices due to improvements in the efficiency of collections only. As such, we modelled low and high NHM prices covering a number of factors that could increase/decrease the lift prices going forward.</p>
              </td>
              <td>
